Maintainer: Dermot Harnett <dermot.harnett@mdc-berlin.de>
Description: RiboseQC is a powerful analysis tool for the analysis of Ribo-seq data, which is able to provide read-length specific analysis of both cytoplasmic and organellar ribosome, and provides interactive visualization of results in a dynamic html report
